
vimconfig

Project of powerful ViM configuration files. ViM is a quality text
editor with huge set of features.

This file is fast howto install this vimconfig.


Copy content of vimconfig/ directory somewhere in your home directory.
Imagine that it will be ~/prog/vimconfig/. Than create symlinks in
root of your home directory:

		cd $HOME
		ln -s prog/vimconfig/vimrc .vimrc
		ln -s prog/vimconfig/vim/ .vim    

Installation is done.

For further updates simply goes to directory ~/prog/vimconfig/ and
type this command:

		cvs update

And that's all folks.


